dc_title_s: EMS Response Districts Vernon County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents Emergency Medical Service (EMS) response districts in Vernon County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This data set consists of digital data depicting the emergency service zones (ESZ) for Vernon County, Wisconsin. The ESZ location were created by overlaying the Ambulance, Fire Department, First Responder, and Jaws, emergency service maps and assign an Emergency Service Number to each unique combination. The zones are used to organize and dispatch emergency services to Vernon County, Wisconsin.]
